            <div class="title">
                Overseas Forces (Home Leave Scheme)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1944-11-17/debates/f5523f61-f28e-4eb1-92d0-810abd22e821/Palestine(TerroristActivities)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
