        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-053f1d95-423a-49f0-911f-8a265c3caec4">
                Captain Peter Macdonald
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-053f1d95-423a-49f0-911f-8a265c3caec4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-11-17/debates/d7b942ec-cf2b-4e4d-8775-c108df82ab6d/OverseasForces(HomeLeaveScheme)#contribution-053f1d95-423a-49f0-911f-8a265c3caec4">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the Prime Minister confirm that the reference to the South East Asia Command includes Burma? As regards the European Forces, is it not a fact that troops are given leave in Paris and Brussels and hospitality is arranged for them?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-053f1d95-423a-49f0-911f-8a265c3caec4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-11-17/debates/d7b942ec-cf2b-4e4d-8775-c108df82ab6d/OverseasForces(HomeLeaveScheme)#contribution-053f1d95-423a-49f0-911f-8a265c3caec4">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-55ecc8fc-e543-4897-9c56-eee382c35838">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-55ecc8fc-e543-4897-9c56-eee382c35838">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-55ecc8fc-e543-4897-9c56-eee382c35838">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-55ecc8fc-e543-4897-9c56-eee382c35838">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-55ecc8fc-e543-4897-9c56-eee382c35838" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-11-17/debates/d7b942ec-cf2b-4e4d-8775-c108df82ab6d/OverseasForces(HomeLeaveScheme)#contribution-55ecc8fc-e543-4897-9c56-eee382c35838">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Of course, it includes Burma; the South East Asia Command, indeed, is principally concerned at this time with Burma. As far as local leave in theatres of war is concerned, that is a matter for the Commanders-in-Chief, and much is done to give a break and change to the officers and men who are in this heavy fighting. But I am looking forward to a period, which I cannot forecast now, when it will be possible to introduce something like a short leave to England scheme from France and Germany such as we had in the last war.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-55ecc8fc-e543-4897-9c56-eee382c35838" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-11-17/debates/d7b942ec-cf2b-4e4d-8775-c108df82ab6d/OverseasForces(HomeLeaveScheme)#contribution-55ecc8fc-e543-4897-9c56-eee382c35838">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
