        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1c64d339-e88c-406d-9f0d-6f530b901962">
                Mr. Kirby
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1c64d339-e88c-406d-9f0d-6f530b901962" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-11-17/debates/d7b942ec-cf2b-4e4d-8775-c108df82ab6d/OverseasForces(HomeLeaveScheme)#contribution-1c64d339-e88c-406d-9f0d-6f530b901962">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">May I ask the right hon. Gentleman if he would be good enough to keep under constant review the position of officers and men on the Western Front <span id="2242" class="column-number" data-column-number="2242"></span> so that they do not get into a state of mind in which they think they are "so near and yet so far"?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1c64d339-e88c-406d-9f0d-6f530b901962" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-11-17/debates/d7b942ec-cf2b-4e4d-8775-c108df82ab6d/OverseasForces(HomeLeaveScheme)#contribution-1c64d339-e88c-406d-9f0d-6f530b901962">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





